	   <tr><td colspan=2>Equipping the glves turns your fists into 9/16 weapons.&nbsp;&nbsp;Not 9/15.  Add the 40% haste and you get 9/13 (since it's 40% damage increase, not 40% delay reduction).  If you also have decent item haste, they'll go down to 9/11.<br><br>At MAX haste, with a Golden Sash of Tranquility, a monk's fists are 9/8.75 weapons.  Not bad, I think...<br><br>As a point of note, the effect is usable even if you're not using your fists -- so take something like the Bo Staff of Trorsmang, off of Hoshkar in VP (40/35 2hb, with a few stats) and, with max haste, you end up with a 40/19 weapon.<br><br>wow.<br><br>So get the gloves!  they're worth it!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
